		None<br>
		<br>
		</p></td>
  </tr>
  <tr>
    <td colspan="3" width="585"><p align="center">
    <font color="#9f3215" face="verdana" size="2">The Kobold Shaman is the only magic casting version of the ape-dogs.  The magic they cast is pretty low level stuff, but it will take out a level 1 or 2 and sometimes a 3 or 4.  They have no incredibly dangerous spells, like root or fire bolt, but be careful and take them out quick as all magic-casting enemies are tougher than they seem.</font></td>
  </tr>
